VS CODE
Instalar desde Ms Store

GIT
PS C:\WINDOWS\System32> winget install --id Git.Git -e --source winget

NOTEPAD ++
PS C:\WINDOWS\System32> winget install --id=Notepad++.Notepad++ -e

NVM
PS C:\WINDOWS\System32> winget install --id=CoreyButler.NVMforWindows -e

NODE
nvm install 22
nvm use v22.21.0

7-ZIP
https://www.7-zip.org/

VC++ REDIST
https://learn.microsoft.com/es-es/cpp/windows/latest-supported-vc-redist?view=msvc-170#latest-supported-redistributable-version
VC_redist.x64.exe

XAMPP
https://sourceforge.net/projects/xampp/files/XAMPP%20Windows/8.2.12/
xampp-portable-windows-x64-8.2.12-0-VS16.zip
Descompactar en c:\Datos\xampp 
Agregar al path: C:\Datos\xampp\php
Ejecutar: C:\Datos\xampp\setup_xampp.bat
Ejecutar: C:\Datos\xampp\xampp-control.exe

